
= NagerIT wants to Encourage humane working conditions in the factories of the electronic industries

URL = https://www.nager-it.de/en/maus


=Description=

"German project called Nager-IT who have produced a "Faire Maus" or Fair Mouse.


They have designed the USB mouse using low carbon materials and have gone to great lengths to source ethically produced components and have pushed for transparency throughout the supply chain (something which is almost non existent in electronic production at the moment)."
(http://openenergymonitor.blogspot.co.uk/2013/08/ethical-and-sustainable-electronics.html)


